definition.value: A cyclohexane-1,2-diol with trans-configuration. It is a metabolite of cyclohexene oxide and other such compounds.
A phytosterol consisting of ergostane having double bonds at the 5,6-, 7,8- and 22,23-positions as well as a 3beta-hydroxy group.
A cyanoamino acid that is the 3-cyano-derivative of L-alanine.
